{"tid":1045762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有沙基利唔用，走去換占士米拿","createTime":"2019-03-03T18:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T02:18:24.000Z","uid":114217,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c17866165bfacfe99270456d1e6abc85601f6ff","tid":1045762,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"短撚出親都有貨交<br />\n唔明點解咁少用佢<br />\n高普好波"},{"pid":"9588a9853d5ca0d340e775cb58e5795963932082","tid":1045762,"uid":85284,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:19:04.000Z","msg":"我觀察咗高普呢幾年嘅言，行，用人，排陣，打法<br />\n呢個人係唔會擺球會利益優先過自己嘅喜好<br />\n佢嗰啲咩嘢 Heavy Metal <br />\n其實就係一渣工兵同雜耍球員喺度胡亂奔跑<br />\n所以中場佢咁鍾意用 Wijnaldum  Milner Can 等等<br />\n最後咪搞到<br />\n猜波又唔夠強隊嘅技術型中場線球員猜<br />\n對住弱隊嘅中場壓逼就大家亂鬥亂<br />\n而高普呢個人又小氣，又記仇<br />\n我諗沙基利都應該係得罪咗佢，情形就好似史杜歷治咁<br />\n喺利物浦有冇得出場，同有冇實力，係冇關係"},{"pid":"0122b170ef438ebc47843f50ea349f3e3b0850ee","tid":1045762,"uid":49836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:15:09.000Z","msg":"由季初到而家都唔明 洗咁多錢改造個中場 點解到而家仲係用緊工兵陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔用不如比哂我廠啦 我肯定發揮得好過猁個工兵陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7700608b412ca10192bd5c814d45108ab83e26","tid":1045762,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/135040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F135040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=274319fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"110b12a15da25784a44f64dff3d451717a05ffc0","tid":1045762,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"上季明明玩迫搶 前場組織好撚勁<br />\n今季買左艾利臣同雲迪克就超級保守 搞到前場啞晒火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />